title: FX Photo Studio 2.8 [Intel/K]
description:
FX Photo Studio Pro is a true powerhouse for creative digital artists of all skill levels. The app features more filters and effects than any other software; plus powerful editing tools and stylish photo frames to make your pictures really worth a thousand words. 

____________________________________________


What's New in Version 2.8
Fx Photo Studio Pro is ready for Mavericks. 
The new version also brings a number of performance improvements and bug fixes, including external display support upgrade and enhanced image processing. 

Thank you for being a user of Fx Photo Studio Pro.
This makes our little team really happy and proud.
Macphun Software.
